{"lemma":"غَسِيلُ","slug":"غَسِيلُ","root":"غ.س.ل","root_slug":"غ-س-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-س-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n31860","n31865"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%8E%D8%B3%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%84%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"washed"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of غَسَلَ (ḡasala) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb","proscribed"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ɣa.siːl/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31860","headword_ar":"غَسِيلٌ","root":"gsl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"magosuwlN","text_ar":"مَغْسُولٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Washed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S, O, Msb, K;) applied to a thing, (S, O,) and to a dead body; (Lh, Msb, TA;) and the former is also applied as an epithet to a fem. n., as is also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasiylapN","text_ar":"غَسِيلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, O, K;) or this last is used after the manner of substs., like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naTiyHapN","text_ar":"نَطِيحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*abiyHapN","text_ar":"ذَبِيحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; not as is said in the S [and O] after the manner of epithets: (IB, TA:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasiylN","text_ar":"غَسِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasoliY","text_ar":"غَسْلِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gusalaA='u","text_ar":"غُسَلَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Lh, K, TA;) and the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasiylapN","text_ar":"غَسِيلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and app. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasiylN","text_ar":"غَسِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"used a fem. epithet] is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasaAlaY","text_ar":"غَسَالَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gusaAlaY","text_ar":"غُسَالَى"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K accord. to different copies.) Han- dhaleh Ibn-er-Ráhib was called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasiylu AlmalaAy^ikapi","text_ar":"غَسِيلُ المَلَايِكَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The washed of the angels"},{"kind":"text","text":"], because he died a martyr on the day of Ohod, and the angels washed him, (S, O, Msb,) accord. to the Prophet, who said that he saw them washing him. (O.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gusalapN","text_ar":"غُسَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b3-  [It is now used as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Clothes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like, put together to be washed."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"}],"source_refs":["S","O","IB","TA","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n31865","headword_ar":"غِسِّيلٌ","root":"gsl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gusalapN","text_ar":"غُسَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}